{"tid":1303255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【CONNECT同行】合法表達意見　政府籲fb及ig提交施政報告建議","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:20:46.000Z","uid":149055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7748f9f3bd5e0ffc108556f88d548a364e620519","tid":1303255,"uid":149055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"2019年施政報告展開公眾諮詢 fb及ig可留言發表意見<br />\n社會 16:31 2019/07/10 <br />\n<br />\n▲ 去年施政報告題為「堅定前行，燃點希望」。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n社會仍處反修例爭議氣氛下，特區政府今（10日）就2019年《施政報告》展開公眾諮詢。行政長官林鄭月娥、政務司司長張建宗和財政司司長陳茂波會陸續與不同界別人士會面，聽取意見。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，要持續發展經濟，改善民生，需要社會一起籌謀，同心協力。她誠邀各位市民就《施政報告》發表意見，讓政府可以集思廣益，制訂切合市民需要的政策措施。她和團隊會虛心聆聽廣大市民的聲音，並在第3份《施政報告》中作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n市民可登入網站（<a href=\"http://www.policyaddress.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.policyaddress.gov.hk&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=0399f68e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.policyaddress.gov.hk</a>）、在2019年《施政報告》公眾諮詢的fb專頁或Instagram留言，亦可透過電郵、電話（2432 1899）或傳真（2537 9083）就施政報告提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2396783/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2396783%2F&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=e20e9aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2396783/</a>"},{"pid":"7d8f280592dd5352c868a1b76a2b1158a79818d7","tid":1303255,"uid":242176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"搞掂左今日區議會先"},{"pid":"fa28f5ddf5b039ea79c4c46ca6240a34beb1b5d9","tid":1303255,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"表佢老母咩 二百萬人走出嚟先叫退一小步 <br />\n而家喺度整色整水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0e269676d11124cedc9eed511c8631baa1a162","tid":1303255,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"要求林鄭落地獄"},{"pid":"999f1475